name: END
description: $END is designed as a digital cryptographic fungible token designed for exclusive use within the Endless Clouds ecosystem. And will be treated as a premium currency across Treeverse, currently available on all major stores. Endless Clouds Foundation is already powering 3 digital collectible collections for the Treeverse ecosystem: Nftrees, Treeverse Plots and Timeless which have done $100M+ in secondary volume.
